{"tid":1859140,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[手足不是condom] 反修例遊行期間慢駛車輛司機涉危駕等罪提訊","createTime":"2020-02-03T06:01:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T06:41:49.000Z","uid":21470,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"24982370a9315e3ebd532057de3326b024f57e17","tid":1859140,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T06:01:51.000Z","msg":"反修例遊行期間慢駛車輛司機涉危駕等罪提訊<br />\n<br />\n去年8月將軍澳有反修例遊行，有車輛在一個迴旋處慢駛，一名私家車司機涉嫌沒跟從指示行駛，令一名警員手部撞傷，下車被捕時一度掙扎，被控危險駕駛和抗拒警務人員，案件在觀塘裁判法院提訊。被告是中港貨車司機，近日從內地回港，控辯雙方出於公眾利益同意被告不用出庭應訊。案件在下月16日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n37歲被告被控去年8月4日，在將軍澳寶琳北路和寶順路交界迴旋處，危險駕駛私家車，並抗拒3名執行職務的警員。被告不能離港，要定期向警署報到。"},{"pid":"e01159ed88b9d7f81eafd7295da2ed6a34227922","tid":1859140,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T06:08:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"680d82f3a5afeb95e97569889b5070bc1758852c","tid":1859140,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T06:27:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7b44f53701752177f599a51dd2eabba053b3868b","tid":1859140,"uid":131667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T06:31:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8e7c26fccc4df7fef7c70f33602085eb1fd0a86","tid":1859140,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T06:39:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9269e4d018b4461153cb160123c3471e8c45b654","tid":1859140,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T06:40:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/07/wFK4H0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F07%2FwFK4H0.png&h=34f10f7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OTqXb0P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%